  "cacheVersion": "2026-03-23-fix-external-link-icons",
  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"overview-of-the-week\">Overview of the Week</h2>\n<p class=\"\">House-sitting for my parents and starting to bring stuff to the storage unit- taking a bit in the peace and quiet to work on some of my personal projects and plan my future a little bit.</p>\n<p class=\"\">I've been writing a lot of code- it would be great to get to a place in a few of my projects in the stage where I need to sketch / design the UX and flow and interactions instead of writing code.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"projects-worked-on\">Projects Worked On</h2>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"scrapbook\">Scrapbook</h3>\n<p class=\"\">Continuing to work on my Scrapbook project, even though I am not sure why, it makes me happy to work on it. But it is difficult to explain the value, or exactly what benefit it will bring me. But I persist.</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"connectology\">Connectology</h3>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721323768/Screen_Recording_2024-07-18_at_1.28.36_PM.mov\" alt=\"Screenshot - - \" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1721323768/Screen_Recording_2024-07-18_at_1.28.36_PM.mov 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1721323768/Screen_Recording_2024-07-18_at_1.28.36_PM.mov 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721323768/Screen_Recording_2024-07-18_at_1.28.36_PM.mov 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1721323768/Screen_Recording_2024-07-18_at_1.28.36_PM.mov 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<p class=\"\">Continuing to play with my Connectology project. Worked on moving the network pan/zoom state to its own composable. This lets me show the network as both SVG and ASCII and still let the user pan and zoom around. Also added some fun sound effects when adding or connecting nodes, or shuffling the position.</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Network diagram showing 14 interconnected nodes labeled NODE 1 through NODE 13, illustrating a distributed system or graph structure with branching pathways.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721239706/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_2.08.14_PM.png\" alt=\"Network diagram showing 14 interconnected nodes labeled NODE 1 through NODE 13, illustrating a distributed system or graph structure with branching pathways.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1721239706/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_2.08.14_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1721239706/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_2.08.14_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721239706/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_2.08.14_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1721239706/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_2.08.14_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Network diagram showing 14 interconnected nodes labeled NODE 1 through NODE 13, illustrating a distributed system or graph structure with branching pathways.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%221046%22%20height%3D%221040%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%201046%201040%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;\" data-placeholder=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%221046%22%20height%3D%221040%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%201046%201040%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" width=\"1046\" height=\"1040\" data-dimensions=\"1046×1040\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figcaption class=\"\">Network diagram showing 14 interconnected nodes labeled NODE 1 through NODE 13, illustrating a distributed system or graph structure with branching pathways.</figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"netlify-dashboard\">Netlify Dashboard</h3>\n<p class=\"\">I have been working on so many projects, it is hard to see the build status of all of them in one place. I took some time to add some information hierarchy to the cards.</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Netlify dashboard displaying deployed web projects including Electology, Connectology, Coachartie showcase, and photo gallery sites with build statuses and deployment timestamps.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721595229/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_4.53.34_PM.png\" alt=\"Netlify dashboard displaying deployed web projects including Electology, Connectology, Coachartie showcase, and photo gallery sites with build statuses and deployment timestamps.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1721595229/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_4.53.34_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1721595229/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_4.53.34_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721595229/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_4.53.34_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1721595229/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_4.53.34_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Netlify dashboard displaying deployed web projects including Electology, Connectology, Coachartie showcase, and photo gallery sites with build statuses and deployment timestamps.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%223824%22%20height%3D%222474%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%203824%202474%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;\" data-placeholder=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%223824%22%20height%3D%222474%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%203824%202474%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" width=\"3824\" height=\"2474\" data-dimensions=\"3824×2474\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figcaption class=\"\">Netlify dashboard displaying deployed web projects including Electology, Connectology, Coachartie showcase, and photo gallery sites with build statuses and deployment timestamps.</figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"creative-endeavors\">Creative Endeavors</h2>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"jzuly-music\">JZULY music</h3>\n<p class=\"\">Josh, Ben, and I took 2 days in the studio to record 30 demos using the live looper. Since then, each of us have 6 songs to polish in Logic, and I spent a bunch of time working on mine.</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Digital audio mixing session with multiple tracks including dialogue, ambient sound effects, and music cues with frequency and volume automation curves.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721572300/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_10.31.24_AM.png\" alt=\"Digital audio mixing session with multiple tracks including dialogue, ambient sound effects, and music cues with frequency and volume automation curves.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1721572300/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_10.31.24_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1721572300/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_10.31.24_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721572300/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_10.31.24_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1721572300/Screenshot_2024-07-21_at_10.31.24_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Digital audio mixing session with multiple tracks including dialogue, ambient sound effects, and music cues with frequency and volume automation curves.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%223824%22%20height%3D%222474%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%203824%202474%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;\" data-placeholder=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%223824%22%20height%3D%222474%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%203824%202474%22%20preserveAspectRatio%3D%22none%22%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3ClinearGradient%20id%3D%22g%22%20x1%3D%220%22%20y1%3D%220%22%20x2%3D%221%22%20y2%3D%221%22%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%220%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23222222%22%2F%3E%3Cstop%20offset%3D%22100%25%22%20stop-color%3D%22%23333333%22%2F%3E%3C%2FlinearGradient%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20height%3D%22100%25%22%20fill%3D%22url(%23g)%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" width=\"3824\" height=\"2474\" data-dimensions=\"3824×2474\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figcaption class=\"\">Digital audio mixing session with multiple tracks including dialogue, ambient sound effects, and music cues with frequency and volume automation curves.</figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"books-movies-tv\">Books, Movies, TV</h2>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\">Deadliest catch’s new season is excellent as always</li>\n<li class=\"\">Really enjoyed JP McDade’s <a href=\"https://youtu.be/s9TOXFM3t1M?si=HcLPNe_hTMI6WIti\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">new special</a></li>\n<li class=\"\">Also liked <a href=\"https://youtu.be/VNGwA9FRrEk?si=9HS0GVaoZrpvVmnz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Nick Swardson’s new special</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"personal-growth--health\">Personal Growth &#x26; Health</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Ben helped me move a bunch of stuff to the storage unit to prepare to move out of my apartment.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"social--community-engagement\">Social &#x26; Community Engagement</h2>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"goals-for-the-future\">Goals for the Future</h2>\n<!-- Set Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-bound goals or intentions for the upcoming week. -->\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Flowchart for extracting relationships from text content using LLM APIs, with branching logic for validation, API selection, and result processing.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1721227993/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_10.53.01_AM.png\" alt=\"Flowchart for extracting relationships from text content using LLM APIs, with branching logic for validation, API selection, and result processing.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1721227993/Screenshot_2024-07-17_at_10.53.01_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v17